<H3>Research, Policy and Other Organizations</H3>
<UL>
<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://calvin.biotech.wisc.edu/jeffries/">The BioEnergy Home Page</A>


<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.greenfuels.org/">Canadian Renewable Fuels Association</A>
