<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.ase.org/pdf/eefpdf3.pdf">Energy Efficiency Financing: A lender's guide for taking advantage of this emerging market</A>- from Alliance to Save Energy <BR><!-- Font Tag --><FONT SIZE=2>to view you need the free <A HREF="http://www.adobe.com/prodindex/acrobat/main.html">Acrobat Reader from Adobe</A></FONT>
<LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.oikos.com/esb/">Energy Source Builder</A>- a bimonthly newsletter
 <LI><!-- Link Tag --><A HREF="http://www.energyusernews.com/">Energy User News</A>

