<a name="fn41">[43]</a> Joint comments of Minnegasco, NSP Gas and NSP Electric
on the Proposed Conservation Improvement Project, "Effective Implementation and
Delivery of Energy-Efficient Technologies and Practices" submitted by the
builders Association of Minnesota, Docket G, E-999/CIP-93-716, September 15,
1993.<p>
<a name="fn42">[44]</a> See note 14.<p>
<a name="fn43">[ ]</a>
 <p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
<p>
