<HTML VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN">
<HEAD><TITLE>Custom Web Page Creation</TITLE></HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#000000" TEXT="#B07743" LINK="#FFF9B0" VLINK="#FFF9B0">
<CENTER><IMG SRC="../images/123.jpg"></CENTER><P><BR>
</P><P><IMG ALIGN="TOP" SRC="../images/button.jpg" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20"> Print and Read over the Homepage Development Process<BR>
<IMG ALIGN="TOP" SRC="../images/button.jpg" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20"> Call us at (505)843-4292 to prepare a customized proposal.<BR>
<IMG ALIGN="TOP" SRC="../images/button.jpg" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20"> Send us your material and we'll do the rest!</P>
<P><BR><IMG SRC="../images/yellbow.gif">
</P><CENTER><H2><I>Homepage Development Process</I></H2></CENTER>

<H3>Initial Homepage Design and Development</H3>

<UL>

<LI>Call us at (505)843-4292 so we can assess your needs and help you develop your web presence.</LI>

<LI>Fax or mail in the &quot;Web Page Proposal Agreement&quot; to initiate the Homepage development process. This 
states the desired package, price and terms of agreement.</LI>

<LI>Send in your 35mm slides or negatives, photos, color brochures, and text information (preferably on disk: Word, WordPerfect, or ASCII) for inclusion in the Homepage.</LI>

<LI>Suggest key words that you want your Homepage to be found under when someone does an Internet search.</LI>

<LI>ATIIN will design and develop the Homepage with your initial input. This includes text and image scanning, layout, and programming for custom bullets and backgrounds.</LI>

<LI>ATIIN will fax you a copy of the Homepage layout and content. A Homepage address is assigned at this point <I>http://www.atiin.com/yourcompany</I> (address is case sensitive)</LI>

</UL>

<H3>Homepage Implementation and Registration</H3>

<UL>

<LI>Upon your approval, ATIIN will implement the Homepage on the Internet and verify that all links work.</LI>

<LI>Your Homepage is now accessible on the Internet.</LI>

<LI>ATIIN will return the materials, that you request, used for development.</LI>

<LI>ATIIN registers your Homepage with key words for search tools on the Internet.</LI>

<LI>Note: Many search tools on the Internet are limited to 80 characters.</LI>

</UL>

<H3>Homepage Storage</H3>

<UL>

<LI>Your Homepage is stored on a state-of-the-art Silicon Graphics server connected to a T2 (1O MB/sec fiberoptic connection) on the Internet.</LI>

<LI>Length of storage depends on the monthly or yearly option lease selected.</LI>

</UL>

<H3>Changes to Homepage</H3>

<UL>

<LI>After the Homepage is implemented, major changes or additions to the Homepage are billed at a $50/hour rate.</LI>

</UL>
</CENTER></BODY></HTML>
