<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HTML VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HEAD><TITLE>Uniband Inc. - An enterprise of the Turtle Mountan Band of Chippewa Indians</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<body background="./logoemb8.gif" >
<IMG align ="left" src="./unilog1a.gif" alt="Logo of Uniband Inc."><H1>Uniband Inc.</H1>
<P>BUSINESS THRIVES ON THE CHIPPEWA RESERVATION</P>

<P>Uniband is located within the boundaries of the Turtle Mountain Indian 
Reservation headquartered in Belcourt, ND. The reservation was 
established by executive order in 1884. It is the reserve and home of 
the Turtle Mountain Band of Chippewa Indians, a federally recognized 
sovereign Indian Tribe.</P>

<MENU>
<LI><A href="./about.htm">About Uniband</A> - Uniband Corporation is a successfully
operated and progressive data entry and technical services business.</LI>

<LI><A href="./services.htm">Services and Clients</A> - Uniband can provide numerous data entry and technical services to various government 
   agencies and private corporations.</LI>

<LI><A href="./employ.htm">Employment Opportunities</A> - our reputable technical services and
Data Entry company has positions available in the Southwest.</LI>
</MENU>
<P></P>
