<CENTER><H2>ADVERTISING</H2></CENTER>

<P>Advertising in Arrowfax Directories offers a unique opportunity to profile your community or Tribal government to other First Nations in North, Central, and South America. It also affords an opportunity to market your products or services to Native American / Inuit/Metis / people wherever they exist. It is networking at it's best. Re-awakening ancestral trading links.</P>

<P></P>

<CENTER><H2>NEW LISTINGS</H2></CENTER>

<P>All listings in the Arrowfax Database are free and limited to Tribal/Inuit/First Nations / American Indian / Metis / Native American / Aboriginal /Indigenous people. Listings are also limited to Governments, Organizations, Institutions, Programs and Businesses. If there are any errors or additions, do not hesitate to contact us.</P>

<P></P>

