<P>This new directory will combine the data of the Provinces of Alberta, Saskatchewan, and Manitoba (CANADA)</P>

<P>Arrowfax over the last three years has expanded to cover the United States and plans to be covering Mexico by the spring of 1996. This is networking at an International level! Recognizing that not everyone operates at the International level, Arrowfax has decided to publish the Prairie Region Directory. This new Directory will contain information that is regional in it's focus.</P>

<P>This will include information such as Native Schools, Names of Leaders, Sports Clubs, Artists, Government Listings, and other regional listings. </P>
