<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HTML VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HEAD><TITLE>Arrow Fax Inc. - Internet Directory First Nations Tribal</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER><IMG SRC="./nations.gif"></CENTER><BR>
<br>
<P>This new directory will cover Internet and E-mail addresses of the First Nations, Tribal Entities, Web Sites, LANS, WANS, and BBS's. This is invaluable for those surfing the web on a regular basis. It allows people to determine what they want, and where they can find it before even logging on, thus saving time and money.</P>

<center><img src="../images/bargreen.gif"></center>
<br>
<IMG align="right" src="./disk.gif" alt="Internet directory disk">
<h2> Get yours today!</h2>

<h2>1. Diskette (High Density).<br>

In convenient to use ASCII (.txt) form<br>

for your computer.<br>

ONLY $50.00<br></h2>
<center><img src="../images/bargreen.gif"></center>
<BR>
<IMG align="right" src="./book.gif" alt="Internet Tribal Directory book">

<h2>2. Easy to use book form<br>

ONLY: $15.00</h2>

