<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>Russell Publications American Indian Marketing and Data Resources</TITLE>
</HEAD> 
<BODY BACKGROUND="mapbg2.jpg">


	<CENTER><IMG SRC="logo1.gif"><BR>
	<P><B><FONT SIZE="+2">R</FONT>USSELL <FONT SIZE="+2">P</FONT>UBLICATIONS</B><BR>
	American Indian Data Resources<BR>
</P></CENTER>


<CENTER><TABLE BORDER WIDTH=90%>
<TR><TD><EM><B>&quot;For a subject worked and reworked so often in novels,
motion pictures and television, American Indians remain probably the least
understood and the most misunderstood Americans of us all&quot;.  </B></EM> 
 President John F. Kennedy  - 1963</P> 
</TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER>
<BR>

<P>Today, there are 2 million Indians - affiliated with 557 tribes -
living on 311 reservations. In addition, each tribe is considered a sovereign
nation, each with its own agenda. The logistics are mind-boggling! </P> 
<P>Before we can address Indian issues or develop any meaningful political strategy, 
we must know the answers to some very basic questions: &quot;What is the size and location of today's
Indian population and reservation land base?&quot; Russell Publications is a resource for this 
information.</P>

<A HREF="map7.jpg"><IMG ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="mapicon.gif"></a>
<menu>
<P><B><Font size=+2>M</FONT>AP OF <Font size=+2>A</font>MERICAN <Font size=+2>I</font>NDIAN <Font size=+2>H</font>ISTORY 
. <br>$15.00 + $4.00 s/h</B></P>
	
<UL>
<LI>24&quot; x 36&quot; full-color laminated map. 	</LI>
<LI>11 BIA Area Office boundaries. 	</LI>
<LI>311 federally recognized reservations. 	</LI>
<LI>211 Gaming reservations indicated. 	</LI>
<LI>337 federally recognized tribes. 	</LI>
<LI>27 state-recognized tribes. 	</LI> 	</UL>
</menu>     

<img src="./roster.jpg" align="left">
<menu><P><B><font size=+2>R</font>ESERVATION <FONT SIZE=+2>R</FONT>OSTER:<br>
$2.00 + $1.00 s/h</B> </P>	
<UL>
<LI>5.5&quot; x 8.5&quot; - 24 pages.</LI>
<LI>Each reservation on the map is listed in the Roster.</LI>
<LI>Roster lists the size and population of each reservation.</LI>
</UL>

</Menu>

<P></P> 

       
<P><B><EM>&quot;In my humble opinion, this is one of the best Indian
maps on the market and should be in the hands of everyone interested in Indians.&quot;
</EM></B>  George Russell, Saginaw Chippewa 1996</P>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/das_bl2.gif">

<P><B>All orders are shipped Priority Mail (2 day delivery)<BR>
 Map and Roster - $16.00 + $4.00 s/h.  Quantity discounts available.</B></P>
