<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Gray &amp; Gray Advertising - What do we do</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><CENTER><TABLE><TR><TD COLSTART="1"><IMG
ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="what1.jpg" VSPACE="0" HSPACE="0"><IMG SRC="what2.jpg"><BR>Gray
and Gray a full-service advertising agency has been helping national clients
like the American Indian College Fund, Tribal College Journal, American Indian
Higher Education Consortium, Indian Health Service, Indian Head Gaming Center,
Isleta Gaming Palace, Santa Fe Community College, Albuquerque Technical
Vocational Institute, National Indian Business Association and Native Americans
in Philanthropy. We have been helping them with their advertising campaigns,
Internet communications, brochures, posters, multimedia presentations,
packaging, magazines, invitations, marketing plans, conference materials, logos
and direct marketing to name a few.</TD></TR></TABLE></CENTER><IMG
SRC="what3.jpg" ALIGN="BOTTOM">
