<HTML><HEAD><TITLE>Gray &amp; Gray Advertising - We have been recognized</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="associat.jpg">
<P><BR>Gray &amp; Gray is member of the New Mexico Advertising Federation,
American Institute of Graphic Artist, Native American Journalist Association,
National Council for Marketing and Public Relations, National Indian Business
Association and the University College Designers Association.</P>
<P>Gray and Gray has been recognized by the following organizations.</P>
<UL><LI>11 National Council for Marketing and Public Relations Awards</LI>
<LI>2 Native American Journalist Awards</LI>
<LI>2 New Mexico Public Relations Association, El Conquistador Awards</LI>
<LI>2 National School of Public Relations Association Awards</LI>
<LI>Print Magazine Award</LI>
<LI>American Association of Museums Award</LI>
<LI>AMR First Place Advertising Award</LI></UL>
