<TITLE>Spirit Ware Home Page</TITLE></HEAD>
<META name="description" content="Spirit Ware is a fully Native-owned company, 
based on the Six Nations Reserve of the Grand River Territory in Ontario, Canada.
For thousands of years Native Americans have been creating beautiful artwork, 
inspired from a spiritual love and reverence for nature. I have tried to capture the 
essence of my own Native heritage by providing the link between the historical historical past 
and the present through the design of the clothing and accessories presented presented in our 
1996 Collection.">
<META name="keywords" content="Aboriginal Business Fashion
Aboriginal Fashion Native Designers
