<BR></PRE><HR>
<P><A HREF="david2.jpg"><IMG ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="david1.jpg" ALT="Jacket"></A></P>
<P><FONT SIZE="+2"><A NAME="BDAVID">B</A></FONT>ETTY <FONT SIZE="+2">D</FONT>AVID
 - SHEARLINGS
<BR></P>
<P>(805) 682-5175
</P>
<P>
Native-made, hand-painted shearling coats.  True collectors' items.  Catalog $5.
 
</P>
<P>All coats are custom made by Betty David, a member of the Spokane Tribe of
Indians.  These shearling jackets are decorated with Northwest Coast Indian
designs in a style shared by over 20 groups of Indians in Alaska, Canada, and
Washington.  Briefly stated, animal and spirit images artistically arranged to
fill the space comprise the Northwest Coast style.  These coats are warm,
beautiful, and made to be worn.  Each jacket is truly one of a kind.  Every
effort is made to fulfill your special requests.</P>
