<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HTML VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HEAD><TITLE>Indian Arts and Crafts Association - Membership</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>
<body background="./logoemb1.gif">
<center><H1>IACA - Membership</H1></center>

<P>IACA currently has more than 700 members in the United States, Canada, Germany, Japan, Italy, and Australia.</P>

<H3>Membership Categories and fees:</H3>

<P></P>

<UL>

<LI><B>Artist/Crafts person</B> - Membership fee: $50.00/year.</LI>

<LI><B>Tribal Enterprises</B> - Membership fee: $175.00/year</LI>

<LI><B>Retail</B> - Membership fee: $175.00/year.</LI>

<LI><B>Wholesale</B> - Membership fee: $175.00/year.</LI>

<LI><B>Wholesale/Retail</B> - Membership fee: $175.00/year.</LI>

<LI><B>Collector</B> - Membership fee: Individual $60.00/year, Joint $90.00/year</LI>

<LI><B>Museum</B> - Membership fee: $50.00/year (Museum Shops: retail membership category)</LI>

<LI><B>Sustaining</B> (Individuals or businesses who support the goals and activities but do not meet the criteria of any other category) - Membership fee: $100.00/year.</LI>

<LI><B>Associate</B> (organizations involved in the Indian arts and crafts industry who wish to support the goals and activities of IACA but do not meet the criteria of any other category) - Membership fee: $100.00/year.</LI>

</UL>

<H3>Application Process</H3>

<P>Information on membership criteria and application procedure is available through the Indian Arts and Crafts Association. Individuals, businesses or organizations may request a membership application by writing or calling the:</P>

<center><P><B>Indian Arts and Crafts Association: <br>122 La Veta NE,<br> Albuquerque, NM 87108<br> 
(505) 265-9149.<BR>fax: (505)265-8251<BR>
email: <a href="mailto:iaca@ix.netcom.com">iaca@ix.netcom.com</B></P></center>

<P></P>
