COLSTART="2"><H1>Indian Arts and Crafts Association Wholesale Markets</H1><P>IACA
conducts two wholesale Indian Arts and Crafts Markets for retailers annually.
All exhibitors in these markets are IACA members, either wholesale dealers or
Indian artists and crafts people. All merchandise exhibited and sold must be
authentic Indian handmade. The buyer will find very high quality work in both
traditional and contemporary styles in all the various forms of Indian arts and
crafts including paintings, textiles, pottery, jewelry, sculpture, carvings,
beadwork, baskets, etc.</P> 
<P><B> IACA Spring Wholesale Indian Arts and Crafts Market:          April
25-27, 1997, Holiday Inn DIA, Denver, Colorado</B></P></TD></TR></TABLE>       
