<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HTML VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HEAD><TITLE>Uniband Inc. - Business Thrives on Chippewa Indian Reservation</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>

<body background="./logoemb6.gif" >
<IMG align="left" src="./logo1.gif" alt="Data Entry Capabilities of Uniband"><center><H2>Uniband Inc.- an enterprise of the Turtle
Mountain Band of the Chippewa Indians</H2>
<img src="../images/line_rai.gif"></center><P><B><I>QUALITY ADP SERVICES AVAILABLE</I></B></P>

<P>Uniband Corporation is a successfully operated and progressive data entry business. Our formula for steady growth has been to hire only well trained and highly skilled data entry operators. Combine this with the most current hardware and software technology and you have a company committed to only top quality data entry work and programming.</P>

<P>Because of our experience and proven efficiency, projects are completed on time and at substantial cost savings to our customers. Stringent quality verification processes guarantee 99.5% error free ADP work.</P>

<P><B><I>FACILITIES AND STAFF</I></B></P>

<P>Uniband utilizes exclusive security, control systems and effective procedures. Every job is given a unique log number along with a specific batch number resulting in strict control procedures. The company employs more than 600 trained data entry operators who are well versed in a variety of ADP procedures.</P>

<IMG align="right" src="./twoguys1.gif" alt="Men working on computers"><P><B><I>STATE OF THE ART EQUIPMENT</I></B></P>

<P>The Uniband facility is equipped with the most advanced data entry software of IBM compatible personal computers. The software has been designed to run on a variety of systems. These diverse capabilities mean that Uniband can pass savings to our customers by efficient utilization of our hardware and software.</P>

<P><B><I>PROJECTS COMPLETED ON TIME</I></B></P>

<P>Uniband is responsive to your timetables. Not only do we meet deadlines but Uniband strives to provide virtual error-free work. This is accomplished with 100% independent key verification and a minimum of 10% random proof checking.</P>

<IMG align="left" src="./class1.gif" alt="Uniband e"><P><B><I>FLEXIBLE AND AFFORDABLE SERVICES</I></B></P>

<P>Innovation is a way of life at Uniband. We can customize our services to meet all your requirements. Our experienced operators' efficiency and accuracy can save you money in all your ADP requirements.</P>

<P></P>

<P><B><I>NATIVE AMERICAN OWNED/OPERATED COMPANY</I></B></P>

<P>Uniband is a minority-owned business. This status can offer certain bidding opportunities that can be advantageous to customers. We will be happy to explain all the particulars of this program.</P>

<IMG align="right" src="./unibldg1.gif" alt="Uniband Data Entry sign on Building"><P><B><I>HERE TO SERVE YOU</I></B></P>

<P>Uniband is ready, willing and able to serve you with all your ADP needs. For a free consultation, <B>please contact us soon.</P>

<P></P>
<Center>

