<TITLE>Santa Clara Pueblo</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER>
<H2>Santa Clara Pueblo </H2>

<TABLE WIDTH=600>
<TR>
<TD ROWSPAN=3 WIDTH=300>

<P>Santa Clara is in its conceptual stages of planning for a Mini Mall type construction. This plan consists of both retail and outlet-type of businesses. The tribe realizes they are in a ideal location to capture a majority of business from Northern New Mexico. Currently Santa Fe is the closest city that has those types of facilities.
Gaming is also part of this lucrative plan which the tribe hopes to get construction going within one year.

</P>
</TD>
<TD WIDTH=300>
