<P></P><H3>Wholesale: <BR><A HREF="sfci2.jpg"><IMG
ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="sfci1.jpg"></A><B><A NAME="santafecrafts">SANTA FE CRAFTS, INC.:</A></B></H3>  <P>Leader in Native American
Indian Arts and Crafts is your best resource for Navajo, Zuni and Santo Domingo
Pueblo jewelry, Hopi kachinas and basketry, Zuni fetishes and a wide variety of
one-of-a-kind objects. 
</P>
<P>We have been buying, selling and researching Native American Indian art for
25 years.  We sell to private collectors, museum stores, catalogs and galleries.
 Let us help you in your quest for specific, unique and rare items.  
</P>
<P><B>Santa Fe Crafts, Inc., P.O. Box 298, Altadena, CA 91003-0298, USA
Telephone: 818.398.1789    Fax: 818.398.1575
</B></P>
