<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HTML 
VERSION="-//IETF//DTD HTML STRICT LEVEL 2//EN"><HEAD>
<TITLE>Tesuque - Day School Renovation</TITLE></HEAD><BODY>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF">

<CENTER>
<H1>Tesuque - Day School Renovation</H1>

<TABLE WIDTH=600>
<TR>
<TD ROWSPAN=2 WIDTH=300>

<P>This is the Tesuque Day School. The school has been renovated once 
before, and has currently been expanded through the use of mobile 
housing due to an increased number of school age children in the 
Tesuque Pueblo. The Pueblo is planning to expand not only the building,
so as to include children from elementary to middle school students, 
but also its curriculum. </P>
<P>The Tesuque Day School is dedicated to preserving and teaching 
traditional Tesuque culture to its children, including instruction in 
the Tewa language.</P>

<P>The plans include additions in the traditional adobe style of 
building, with the necessary improvements in the infrastructure.</P>

<P>Tesuque Pueblo has also used gaming proceeds to hire additional 
rangers to patrol mountain areas and fishing ponds within the Pueblo. 
The tribe is also setting up scholarship programs for tribal students. 
Tesuque realizes the future of its tribe depends on the education of its 
youth. Gaming revenues will finance the educational future of the children 
of Tesuque.
</P>

</TD>

<TD WIDTH=300>
<CENTER><a href="./tes3b.jpg"><IMG src="./tes3a.gif" ></a></CENTER>
<BR>
<CENTER>
<P><I>Historic Tesuque Day School, scheduled for renovation and expansion 
using gaming dollars.</I></P></CENTER></TD>
<TR>
<TD WIDTH=300>
<CENTER><A HREF="./tes4b.jpg"><img src="./tes4a.gif"></a></CENTER>
<BR>
<center>
<P><I>Mobile housing expansion of Day School. After renovation, 
Tesuque Day School will be completely adobe and will serve the 
children of Tesuque.</I></P></center>
</TD>
</TR>
</TABLE>
<H4>| <a href="./tesuque3.htm">More on Tesuque Pueblo</a> | <a href="../nmiga/">Return back to Index</a> | </h4>

</CENTER>
