<DOCHDR>
http://www.atiin.com:80/navajoland/welcome.htm 204.134.95.1 19970115085835 text/html 4659
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0a
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 08:58:31 GMT
