<DD><P>Native American Tourism Center (602) 945-0771<BR>New Mexico Department of Tourism (505) 827-7400</P></DD></DL><P><B>NOTE:  The Navajo Nation is on daylight savings time beginning April and ending October.</B><BR></P><CENTER><P><B>Navajo Tourism Department <BR>P.O. Box 663 <BR>Window Rock, AZ  86515
