<P><A HREF="http://www.atiin.com/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0"> ATIIN,
Incorporated</A>    - <B><I>'atiin</I></B>
- a Navajo word for roadway or pathway - provides Internet and World Wide Web
Technologies and Services.</P>
<P><A HREF="../grayngray/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0"> Gray and Gray</A>
   - is a Native American owned, award winning full service advertising,  design
and marketing firm based in Albuquerque, New Mexico.</P>  
<P><A HREF="../arrowfax/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0"> Arrowfax, Inc.</A>
  - founded to enlarge and promote communication among Native Americans with
over 14,800 U.S. and Canadian listings. . 
</P> 
<P><A HREF="http://www.DiscoverNA.org"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0"> Discover Native America</A>
  - Once you see the Discover Native America performers you'll agree that you have just witnesses the finest gathering of Native American Dancers and performers ever assembled, in one place.</P><P><A
HREF="../mccracken/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0"></A>
<A HREF="../mccracken/">McCracken Computer Art</A>   - specializes in High
quality, professional color laser prints matted and ready for 11&quot; x 14&quot;
frames.</P>
 
<P><A HREF="../russell/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0" ALIGN="left">Russell
Publications</A>   - The map of &quot;American Indian History&quot; and its &quot;Reservation
Roster&quot; provide the facts about today's Native American population, tribes,
and reservations.
</P> 
<P><A HREF="../spiritware/"><IMG SRC="smeagle.gif" BORDER="0">
Spiritware</A>   - Providing the link between the historical past  and the
present through the design of the clothing and accessories presented in our 1996
Collection. </P>






