<HEAD>
<TITLE>Isleta Gaming Palace Overview</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BACKGROUND="../images/parch.gif">
<CENTER><H1><A NAME="top"><FONT SIZE="+3">I</FONT>sleta <FONT SIZE="+3">G</FONT>aming <FONT
SIZE="+3">P</FONT>alace <FONT SIZE="+3">O</FONT>verview</A></H1></CENTER>
<IMG ALIGN="LEFT" SRC="./images/igpbroc1.jpg" VSPACE="5" HSPACE="20">
<P><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="./images/redchip.gif"><B> Isleta Gaming Palace</B> is a majestic gaming palace featuring 30,000 square feet of action-packed entertainment and thrill-a-minute fun in the largest casino center in New Mexico. With more games and more winners, you'll see why Isleta Gaming Palace is more fun! 
</P><P><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="./images/redchip.gif"><B> </B><B>Entertainment fit for a king.</B> Stop in for an exciting game of Poker, Video Poker, Keno, Isleta &quot;21&quot; or Pull Tabs. Isleta Gaming Palace has more action, with nearly 300 video machines waiting to pay off. If Keno is more your style, play &quot;Do It Yourself&quot; <BR>
 &#149; an exciting game of chance in which you pick 8 numbers from the bingo batch. If they come up within the first 20 numbers called, you could be the big jackpot winner! 
</P><P><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="./images/redchip.gif"><B> </B><B>Win a Million Dollars with Mega Bingo.</B> Let us turn your dream of winning a million dollars into a reality with Mega Bingo &#149; the newest game at Isleta Gaming Palace. You'll compete with players in casinos across the country for your chance at a daily jackpot of one million dollars. 
</P><P><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="./images/redchip.gif"><B> </B><B>A Majestic Atmosphere.</B> You won't find the usual folding chairs and dimly-lit shopping center space at Isleta Gaming Palace. Our modern palace features 1,200 comfortable swivel chairs in a virtually smoke-free, clean air environment. And if you're hungry, stop by our restaurant for a quick snack or full meal &#149; you'll find a complete menu to satisfy even the most discriminating taste. 
</P><P><IMG ALIGN="BOTTOM" SRC="./images/redchip.gif"><B> </B><B>New Mexico's Premier Palace of Poker.</B> Come try your luck at a hand of Poker at New Mexico's premier palace of poker. You'll love Texas Hold 'Em, Caribbean Stud Poker and classic Stud Poker. If 21 is your game of choice, Isleta Gaming Palace really is your place, and you'll see why we say 
</P><H1></H1>
