<li> An honor student falls victim to the <a href="/nationalreview/outrage/outrage.html">War on (non-prescription) Drugs</a>. Read about it in National Review's <a href="/nationalreview/outrage/outrage.html">Outrage du Jour</a>.

</ul> 



