<DOCHDR>
http://www.empower.org:80/atr/blackwell.html 204.71.237.79 19970209170050 text/html 5690
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Sunday, 09-Feb-97 17:01:38 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 21-Jan-97 15:30:34 GMT
